# .dockerignore for local-core
# 排除 cloud playbook packs 和其他不需要的文件

# ============================================
# Cloud Playbook Packs (必须排除)
# ============================================
# 排除所有 cloud 相关的 playbook packs
# 这些路径通过 CapabilityInstaller 安装，不应进入 local-core image
**/playbook-packs/**
backend/playbooks/packs-cloud/**
backend/packs/cloud/**
# ⚠️ 关键：排除 cloud capability packs 的安装位置
backend/app/capabilities/**
web-console/src/app/capabilities/**
# 如果存在其他 cloud pack 目录，也排除
backend/app/services/cloud_providers/**
backend/app/services/cloud_sync/**

